  <brief_title>An Efficacy and Safety Study of Gevokizumab in Treating Active Ulcers of Pyoderma Gangrenosum</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled Study of the Efficacy and Safety of Gevokizumab in Treating Active Ulcers of Pyoderma Gangrenosum</official_title>
  <sponsors>
